HTML5 White-Noise Sleep Mixer

Usage

Open index.html in your browser (via file://). Toggle ambient loops and binaural beats, adjust volumes and frequencies to suit your mood.

Features

  • Looped rain & fire sounds
  • Adjustable binaural beats (20–2000 Hz base, 0.1–40 Hz beat)
  • Independent volume sliders

Dependencies

  • No external libraries or servers
  • Audio embedded via Base64 URIs (avoids CORS)

Use Cases

  • Sleep aid / relaxation
  • Focus & meditation background
